 },
 {
  "text": "Érica! Join me for lunch? I always eat at this time.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_erica_join_me_for_lunch_i_always_eat_at_this_tim.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Thank you, David! I usually have lunch at one, but today I am early.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_thank_you_david_i_usually_have_lunch_at_one_but.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Tell me your secret. You always have so much energy! What is your routine?",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_tell_me_your_secret_you_always_have_so_much_ener.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I wake up at seven. I have breakfast — coffee and fruit — and I start work at eight.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_i_wake_up_at_seven_i_have_breakfast_coffee_and_f.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "At seven! I never wake up before seven thirty. My routine starts late.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_at_seven_i_never_wake_up_before_seven_thirty_my.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "And I always sleep early, at ten thirty. Sleep is important, David!",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_and_i_always_sleep_early_at_ten_thirty_sleep_is.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I usually sleep after midnight. Maybe that is my problem!",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_i_usually_sleep_after_midnight_maybe_that_is_my.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Then here is a challenge for you: sleep early tonight!",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_then_here_is_a_challenge_for_you_sleep_early_ton.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Ha! Challenge accepted! And the weekend? Do you relax?",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_ha_challenge_accepted_and_the_weekend_do_you_rel.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Yes! On Sundays my family usually has lunch together. I love it.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_yes_on_sundays_my_family_usually_has_lunch_toget.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Good morning! It is Ana again. My mornings are simple. I always wake up at six. I usually walk in the park before breakfast. Then I have coffee and toast, and I read the news. I never check my phone before breakfast. It is my golden rule. At eight thirty, I start work. I love my calm mornings.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello! Carlos here. My evenings are my favorite time. I usually finish work at six. Then I often cook dinner with my mother. She is the real chef! After dinner, we sometimes watch a movie. I rarely go out at night. At eleven, I go to sleep. A simple evening, a happy life.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_listening2.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I wake up at seven. I have breakfast with coffee and fruit. I start work at eight. I have lunch at one. I always sleep early, at ten thirty.",
